OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny patchy low cloud first
OL,6,Fthing this morning will soon burn off
OL,7,Fleaving a dry, bright day with some
OL,8,Fsunny spells. Clouding over for
OL,9,Fwestern Argyll later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry, bright and warm
OL,12,Fevening for the Glasgow area and
OL,13,Fremaining dry through the night.
OL,14,FCloudier for Argyll with some mist
OL,15,Fpatches, clearing later.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FEarly morning cloud soon
OL,18,Fburning off to leave another very warm
OL,19,Fand largely sunny day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
