OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FHot
OL,6,Fon Thursday but with the risk of heavy
OL,7,Fand thundery outbreaks of rain later
OL,8,Fin the day and into Friday. Fresher by
OL,9,FSaturday but risk of showers.
